---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import H1 from '@components/H1.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <article>
    <H1 scale={true}>Hey! I'm Tijs</H1>
    <section>
      <div>
        <img src='/images/tijs.jpg' alt='Tijs' />
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2>A bit about me</h2>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aut eveniet id dolorum ipsa quidem repellendus est non atque
          fugit, cumque numquam ullam qui voluptate nobis amet nesciunt temporibus consectetur. Animi officiis quo doloribus
          deserunt modi recusandae reiciendis veniam molestias dolore? Ullam sit impedit asperiores molestias repudiandae saepe.
          Ab praesentium saepe obcaecati consequuntur iure, velit sapiente aspernatur impedit adipisci molestiae reprehenderit.
          Dolorum nemo voluptas enim.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

  <style lang='scss'>
    article {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-5);
    }

    section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 320px) minmax(50%, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-5);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
